)Body Expand(\\)
%Tutorial -\-\(~PDSE V2 Member Generations%)\-\- Tutorial
%Command ===>_ZCMD                                                             +
%
%  MAIL or M &m1
`
`  E-Mail the member using the XMITIP e-mail application.
`
`  The XMITIP ISPF dialog will allow the member to be sent as
`  plain text, HTML, PDF, or RTF.
`
)Init
 .cursor = &zcmd
 if (&mail = 1)
    &m1 = ''
 if (&mail = 0)
    &m1 = 'Not enabled.'
)PROC
